\par Characters do not echo to the screen or cause a beep when you type your password so that nearby users won't be able to tell how many letters are in your password.\page {\fs18\up6 ${\footnote \pard\plain \s245\li120\sb80\sl-240 \f3\fs20\lang1033 {
