\par This usually means that you just clicked on the OK button or pressed Enter without typing your username.\page {\fs18\up6 ${\footnote \pard\plain \s245\li120\sb80\sl-240 \f3\fs20\lang1033 {\fs18\up6 $} Kerberos Error 81}} {\fs18\up6 #{\footnote 
