\par Usually caused by a typo with a comma or an extra period. See {\uldb Kerberos Names}{\v ID_HELP_NAMES} for more information on valid name formats.\page {\fs18\up6 ${\footnote \pard\plain \s245\li120\sb80\sl-240 \f3\fs20\lang1033 {\fs18\up6 $}
