\par 
\par Can't lock ticket file.
\par 
\par This error message means that the Kerberos DLL cannot access the memory reserved by {\uldb kerbmem}{\v ID_HELP_SHARE_TICKETS}. This problem can occur under any of three conditions:
\par \pard \fi-600\li720\sb80\sl-240 1.\tab You are running a misbehaved Kerberized application.
